title: #376: My 2019 Year in Review (a solocast)
itunes:title: My 2019 Year in Review: A Solo Cast
description: 2019 was a great year for me. They're all great years, to be honest. But 2019 was no different. Come along as I go over all my favorite podcasts, standup shows, travels, and details of another year where I'm lucky to be doing something I love.
